#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:2
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Some Fundamentals"
msgstr "Inyandiko soko"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:4
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwrite; and many other &katepart; users are very simple to use. Anyone that "
"has used a text editor should have no problems."
msgstr ""
"&kwrite; ni Byoroheje Kuri Koresha . Byakoreshejwe A Umwandiko Muhinduzi "
"Oya . "

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Gukurura no Kurekura"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:12
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&katepart; uses the &kde; Drag and Drop protocol. Files may be dragged and "
"dropped onto &katepart; from the Desktop, the filemanager &dolphin;, or some "
"remote &FTP; site opened in one of &dolphin;'s windows."
msgstr ""
"&kwrite; i &kde; na Porotokole . Gicurasi na &kwrite; Kuva: i , &konqueror; "
"Cyangwa &Bya kure: &FTP; &Ipaji in Rimwe Bya &konqueror; ' S Windows . "

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:22
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many of the shortcuts are configurable by way of the <link linkend="
"\"settings-help-menu\">Settings</link> menu. By default &katepart; honors "
"the following shortcuts:"
msgstr ""
"Bya i Urufunguzo Ibyafataranyijwe ( Amahinanzira ) ku Bya i <link linkend="
"\"settings\"> </link> Ibikubiyemo . Mburabuzi &kwrite; i Urufunguzo "
"Ibyafataranyijwe . "

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ins;"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:30
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle between Insert and Overwrite mode. When in insert mode the editor "
"will add any typed characters to the text while pushing along any data to "
"the right of the text cursor. Overwrite mode causes the entry of each "
"character to eliminate the character immediately to the right of the text "
"cursor."
msgstr ""
"hagati na Gusimbuza Ubwoko . in Ongeramo Ubwoko i Muhinduzi &Ongera Icyo ari "
"cyo cyose Inyuguti Kuri i Umwandiko Icyo ari cyo cyose Ibyatanzwe Kuri i "
"Iburyo: Bya i Umwandiko indanga . Gusimbuza Ubwoko i Icyinjijwe Bya "
"Inyuguti: Kuri i Inyuguti: Ako kanya Kuri i Iburyo: Bya i Umwandiko "
"indanga . "

